# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/partner-content/berkeley-digital/accounting-procedures-recording-transactions-financial/accounting-cycle-recording-transactions/a/the-seven-stages-of-the-basic-accounting-cycle">http://translate.khanacademy.org/partner-content/berkeley-digital/accounting-procedures-recording-transactions-financial/accounting-cycle-recording-transactions/a/the-seven-stages-of-the-basic-accounting-cycle</a>.
