# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/partner-content/berkeley-digital/intro-financial-accounting/need-for-financial-information/a/financial-information-an-overview">http://translate.khanacademy.org/partner-content/berkeley-digital/intro-financial-accounting/need-for-financial-information/a/financial-information-an-overview</a>.
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: es)
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: lol)
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "Businesses engage in a vast range of transactions and activities.  For large businesses like McDonalds and Walmart, transactions could number in the millions per day.  This level of activity gives rise to a large amount of data which is captured by a variety of computer and paper based systems within the company."
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/partner-content/berkeley-digital/intro-financial-accounting/need-for-financial-information/a/financial-information-an-overview">http://translate.khanacademy.org/partner-content/berkeley-digital/intro-financial-accounting/need-for-financial-information/a/financial-information-an-overview</a>.
